<seg id="554">4.5.3 Control management of large tax entities</seg>
<seg id="555">Both SAIs decided not to examine individual cases of VDS inspections carried out, but focused on management issues in order to provide an overview of how tax administrations manage the issue of VAT controls in VDS.</seg>
