<seg id="559">• Are there any statistics or records of rates distinguishing between combating VAT fraud and controlling VAT in general?</seg>
<seg id="560">Czech Republic: No, ADIS does not allow such resolution with the current data version.</seg>
<seg id="561">Germany: The tax administration does not distinguish between the control proposed to combat VAT fraud and the general control of VAT.</seg>
